00:00:34,041 --> 00:00:35,666
has Academy City bustling.

3
00:00:35,750 --> 00:00:37,583
Which gives the Catholic
Church the perfect chance

4
00:00:37,666 --> 00:00:40,541
to conduct a transaction
involving a powerful relic.

5
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:43,291
[KAMIJO] To obtain the
Stab Sword, they are using

6
00:00:43,375 --> 00:00:45,208
a courier named
Oriana Thomson.

7
00:00:45,291 --> 00:00:48,750
And I may have just accidentally
come into contact with her.

8
00:00:51,000 --> 00:01:01,000
♪ [Opening Song] ♪

9
00:02:26,416 --> 00:02:29,041
[beeping]

10
00:02:29,125 --> 00:02:31,416
[dial tone]

11
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:33,416
Kami, hey.
How's it goin'?

12
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:35,625
[TSUCHIMIKADO] As we speak,
I've got eyes on a spot

