I think it'll definitely be
safer for you to remain here...

62
00:05:13,208 --> 00:05:15,666
But I'm talking about
my safety, not yours.

63
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:17,166
Aghhh.

64
00:05:26,083 --> 00:05:28,083
These are decoys.
She's just buying time.

65
00:05:28,166 --> 00:05:30,291
