so let me remind you...

177
00:10:32,208 --> 00:10:34,583
There are many lives
at stake in this battle.

178
00:10:34,666 --> 00:10:35,916
[TSUCHIMIKADO]
It's that serious...

179
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,666
The entire world
may even be at risk.

180
00:10:39,166 --> 00:10:40,666
[STIYL] Let's get on with it.

181
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:41,458
[gasps]

182
00:10:41,541 --> 00:10:42,625
No, Stiyl you can't!

183
00:10:42,708 --> 00:10:44,666
Now is not the time
to worry about me...

184
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:47,916
If I can put a stop to all this,
it's a small price to pay.

185
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,375
But if I do it, you had
damn well better pinpoint

186
00:10:50,458 --> 00:10:52,208
the location of
the intercept spell.

187
00:10:52,291 --> 00:10:53,791
I know your terms.

188
00:10:53,875 --> 00:10:56,916
We must preserve the life Index
leads here in Academy City...

189
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,750
That was your
stipulation, wasn't it?

190
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:06,500
[STIYL] Toma Kamijo...
I am not entirely pleased

191
00:11:06,583 --> 00:11:08,791
with the fact that you
are here right now...

192
00:11:08,875 --> 00:11:11,166
It seems like you
ought to be at her side.

193
00:11:11,250 --> 00:11:13,416
If this ends in
sadness for her...

194
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:15,916
It will be your fault.

195
00:11:19,250 --> 00:11:23,375
[STIYL screaming]

196
00:11:29,833 --> 00:11:33,375
♪

197
00:11:33,458 --> 00:11:34,875
[INDEX] Oooh...

198
00:11:34,958 --> 00:11:36,958
