202
00:11:42,666 --> 00:11:44,125
[KOMOE] Oh,
come on now, sister!

203
00:11:44,208 --> 00:11:46,125
There's no need to
be so disheartened...!

204
00:11:46,208 --> 00:11:47,541
I'm sure he must've had some

205
00:11:47,625 --> 00:11:50,541
important reason for
running off like he did!

206
00:11:51,291 --> 00:11:52,750
Errr.

207
00:11:52,833 --> 00:11:54,875
[sighs]

208
00:11:54,958 --> 00:11:56,541
[FUKIYOSE] That guy's
getting on my last nerve!

209
00:11:56,625 --> 00:11:59,625
I take my eyes off him for
one second, and he disappears.

210
00:11:59,708 --> 00:12:01,500
I mean, honestly! Uh.

211
00:12:01,583 --> 00:12:03,083
[FUKIYOSE] What's the matter?

212
00:12:03,166 --> 00:12:04,958
Oh, hi, Fukiyose!

213
00:12:05,041 --> 00:12:06,541
Is there something
wrong with that girl?

214
00:12:06,625 --> 00:12:08,208
Does she need
some first aid?

215
00:12:09,416 --> 00:12:11,458
