220
00:12:17,958 --> 00:12:20,541
But I think this is something
I can handle on my own.

221
00:12:20,625 --> 00:12:22,208
[FUKIYOSE]
Okay, if you're sure.

222
00:12:23,041 --> 00:12:24,875
[INDEX] Where's Toma?

223
00:12:24,958 --> 00:12:27,958
All I want to know is
where he could've gone?

224
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,041
[TSUCHIMIKADO] Here it comes.

225
00:12:33,125 --> 00:12:35,583
The divination circle is
beginning to respond now...

226
00:12:35,666 --> 00:12:36,875
Hey, Kami!

227
00:12:36,958 --> 00:12:38,708
[TSUCHIMIKADO]
You have a map don't you?

228
00:12:39,125 --> 00:12:40,000
[TSUCHIMIKADO]
Yeah... you know...

229
00:12:40,083 --> 00:12:42,458
that GPS map on
your cell phone?

230
00:12:42,541 --> 00:12:44,458
Well, come on. Bring it here.

231
00:12:44,541 --> 00:12:45,875
[KAMIJO] Tsuchimikado!

232
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:48,875
How can you be so
calm about all of this?!

233
00:12:48,958 --> 00:12:51,791
Stiyl is being tormented
repeatedly all because of you!

234
00:12:51,875 --> 00:12:52,958
Stay cool...

235
00:12:53,041 --> 00:12:55,166
He is a professional
magician, you know.

236
00:12:55,250 --> 00:12:57,083
He's got enough
attack resistance to

237
00:12:57,166 --> 00:12:59,125
handle this spell,
and he knows it.

238
00:12:59,208 --> 00:13:00,708
[shaky exhale]

239
00:13:00,791 --> 00:13:03,125
[KAMIJO] What's going on?
You're bleeding!

240
00:13:03,208 --> 00:13:04,583
The divination circle...

241
00:13:04,666 --> 00:13:06,916
responds to the magic
power of incoming spells,

242
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,750
allowing us to determine
their distance and direction.

243
00:13:09,833 --> 00:13:11,791
[TSUCHIMIKADO] Obviously,
such a handy little tool

244
00:13:11,875 --> 00:13:13,875
can't be activated
without the expenditure

